{"type": "article", "id": 3323, "title": "一个插画师的创作经历", "description": "Best On The Web 是一个推荐性栏目，每个工作日我们会从互联网世界中找出最好看的内容，希望这个栏目让我们始终与阅读、知识和美好在一起。", "date": "2014-11-06T08:07:22Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 4011, "name": "Jean Jullien"}, {"id": 2485, "name": "illustration"}, {"id": 2059, "name": "插画"}, {"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}], "category": 12, "column": null, "author": 13, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143922Sfk7iULqX4Hjh8VN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tJean Jullien 是我很喜欢的一位插画师，画风有爱又有梗，有时候带有些法式小清新。你可以在 instagram 上找到他 <strong><a href=\"http://instagram.com/jean_jullien\" target=\"_blank\">@Jean_Jullien</a> 。</strong><b><a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/jean-jullien-film\" target=\"_blank\">这里的一个短片</a></b><a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/jean-jullien-film\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">展现了他工作时候的样子，突然看到那些作品背后的创作故事不亚于揭露一个魔术背后的秘密，至于创造力这回事，终究还是很难效仿。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">他只喜欢用刷子画画，这种工具让他觉得非常人性化，而且稍不留心就很容易出错。虽然那些作品有的看上去太平常了，和你在一些网站上看上去的没什么两样，但是如果你仔细看到这部短片中他创作时候自信的样子，就会感受到他的不同之处。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143918TMWAD9LSvFz7NO1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143918Ra7IETpCuByKhgo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143919EZfdKz9iLj1Q5bge.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t下面是一些 Jean 眼中的都市人的生活状态。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061439190Moe6KgS7uOCGXLz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061439209R65OKBbZFeAjt0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143920nwHk0hr3x1BECY7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4234375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143921VOjmTxILlA3F9rp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5234375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143921t4vsramwSRnfjzFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143921ogEpxH1AfrabJVvG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}